    <div data-cid="5195847">
        <div class="main review-item" id="5195847">

            
    
    <header class="main-hd">
        <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/36554075/" class="avator">
            <img width="24" height="24" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u36554075-10.jpg">
        </a>

        <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/36554075/" class="name">王小新要快乐</a>

            <span class="allstar30 main-title-rating" title="还行"></span>

        <span content="2011-12-02" class="main-meta">2011-12-02 21:32:12</span>


            <span class="publisher right">
                <a class="publisher" target="_blank" href="https://book.douban.com/subject/5361285/">新世界出版社2010版</a>
            </span>
    </header>


            <div class="main-bd">

                <h2><a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5195847/">结束亦或是开始</a></h2>

                <div id="review_5195847_short" class="review-short" data-rid="5195847">
                    <div class="short-content">

                        从图书馆借回这本书，主要是冲着“蔡骏”两字。依稀记得看过《荒村公寓》还不知道是《幽灵客栈》。所以选择了这本书。读书的过程中我发现我衔接不上故事的背景。情节很模糊了。但我记得看过蔡骏的《蝴蝶公墓》和《诅咒》。在此不加与评价。 这本书给我印象最深的不是小说的故事...

                        &nbsp;(<a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5195847-copy" class="unfold" title="展开">展开</a>)
                    </div>
                </div>

